be able to track them down.

374
00:26:01,851 --> 00:26:02,978
It is like the golden hour.

375
00:26:04,187 --> 00:26:05,939
I know that I shouldn't be doing this,

376
00:26:06,815 --> 00:26:08,858
but please understand just this once.

377
00:26:13,613 --> 00:26:15,073
I get why you have to do this,

378
00:26:17,867 --> 00:26:20,912
but it's time for you
to make up your mind.

379
00:26:22,747 --> 00:26:25,917
Whether you'll stay a professor
or go back to being a detective.

