instead of learning to solve them.

466
00:33:44,939 --> 00:33:48,568
So later on, I got to a point
where I knew the answers right away

467
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:52,447
without understanding
why they were the correct answers.

468
00:33:58,202 --> 00:33:59,871
Another family
where the mom's the problem.

