498
00:36:22,763 --> 00:36:25,183
But my mom was poor,

499
00:36:26,559 --> 00:36:28,561
so I was afraid
she would take all the blame.

500
00:36:31,063 --> 00:36:34,275
That's why I told the judge
that they were all in it together.

501
00:36:36,485 --> 00:36:37,612
That my mom was involved in it too.

502
00:36:40,865 --> 00:36:43,117
I only said that to protect my mom,

503
00:36:45,161 --> 00:36:47,246
but I think I only protected my mom,

504
00:36:48,623 --> 00:36:49,999
not others.

505
00:36:57,340 --> 00:36:58,299
Hey. Please do this for us.

506
00:36:58,382 --> 00:37:01,510
A guy like me can never
make that kind of money.

507
00:37:01,594 --> 00:37:02,637
But you can.

508
00:37:02,720 --> 00:37:04,722
Please forgive them just this once.

509
00:37:05,306 --> 00:37:06,599
